SANDBOX (ISB OSB): set of file that travell with the job

DATA DRIVEN VS CPU DRIVEN
If the resources is chosen based on where the data or the cpu is avaible

COMPUTING MODEL
WMS (workload managment system): 
	-select and rank resources 
	-distribute job

MODEL
-PUSH(eager)
	-job bound to a resource
	-one WMS done the job is sent to that resourec

-PULL \ PILOT(lazy)
	-WMS retain job in queue
	-when resource free take job from queue



PROLOGUE
-prepare for job
-dependecy
EPILOGUE
-return
-final check

SUBMISSION
-WMS
-direct

PILOT JOB SUBMISSION
-advantages: bypass the priority set by the site admins
-disadvantages
